                    <WebAddress>https://www.bop.gov/foia/index.jsp#tabs-1</WebAddress>
                </FooterDetails>
                <Header/>
                <Paragraph>The BOP posts records online. Before filing a formal FOIA request, an information seeker should visit the BOP's "Freedom of Information" web page and view the records section to ensure that the desired information is not already freely accessible.</Paragraph>
